---
// /for-dental/ — vertical lander for independent dental practices (Phase 5, 2026-05-04)
// Dollar impact rationale: $500K-$1.5M dormant LTV per practice (Dental Economics 2025)
// Vocabulary: hygiene recall, treatment-plan completion, dormant patients, hygiene-to-doctor handoff
// Stack: Open Dental, Dentrix, ClearDent, Curve. ADA + provincial colleges advertising rules.
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="For independent dental practices &mdash; Recall, reactivate, complete treatment plans"
  description="AI customer lifecycle for independent dental practices across Canada and the United States. Hygiene recall, dormant-patient reactivation, treatment-plan completion, post-op review automation. Wraps around Open Dental, Dentrix, ClearDent, Curve. HIPAA BAA on request. A service of Agni Consulting."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="ai-hero">
    <p class="ai-eyebrow">FOR INDEPENDENT DENTAL PRACTICES</p>
    <h1>Your dormant patient list is worth <br>$500K&ndash;$1.5M.<br>You&rsquo;ve never reached out.</h1>
    <p class="ai-lead">
      The average independent dental practice has 600&ndash;1,400 patients who haven&rsquo;t been in for 18+ months. At an average lifetime value of $800&ndash;$1,200 per patient, that&rsquo;s $500K&ndash;$1.5M sitting dormant in Open Dental, Dentrix, ClearDent, or Curve. Most practices have never run a single reactivation campaign. Hygiene recall fires from the software but doesn&rsquo;t follow up. Treatment plan completion sits below 50% in most practices.
    </p>
    <p class="ai-lead" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--tx);">
      We run hygiene recall, dormant-patient reactivation, treatment-plan completion, and post-op review automation on autopilot. Wraps around your existing PMS. HIPAA BAA on request. Done-for-you, by operators.
    </p>
    <div class="ai-cta-row">
      <a class="ai-btn" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book a free Growth Audit &rarr;</a>
      <a class="ai-btn-ghost" href="/engagements/">Engagement shapes</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain bullets -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow">Sound like your practice?</p>
      <h2>The dormant iceberg.</h2>
      <ul class="ai-painlist" style="font-size:17px;margin-top:24px;">
        <li>"Our hygiene recall fires emails out of Dentrix. Nobody answers them. We don&rsquo;t follow up."</li>
        <li>"There are 1,200 names in our system who haven&rsquo;t been in since 2023. We&rsquo;ve never run a reactivation."</li>
        <li>"Half of our diagnosed treatment plans never get scheduled. The patient leaves and we forget."</li>
        <li>"We send one review request the day of the appointment. Most patients don&rsquo;t see it. Our review count is stuck."</li>
        <li>"After-hours calls go to voicemail. The competing chain across the street has 24/7 booking."</li>
        <li>"Our front desk turns over every 18 months. The recall script is in someone&rsquo;s head, not in a system."</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top:32px;color:var(--tx-soft);font-size:16px;">
        None of this is dentistry. It&rsquo;s operations &mdash; and operations gets the leftovers in every independent practice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What we run -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">What we run for you</p>
      <h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Five systems. Wraps around your PMS. Respects college advertising rules.</h2>
      <div class="ai-grid-2">

        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>1. Hygiene recall + reactivation</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--tx-soft);">Pulls your overdue list from Open Dental / Dentrix / ClearDent / Curve. Multi-touch SMS + email recall sequences with timed follow-up. Separate sequences for 6-month overdue, 12-month, 18-month+ dormant. Books appointments straight into your PMS calendar.</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Multi-cohort recall sweeps</li>
            <li>Dormant-patient win-back ($500K-$1.5M opportunity per practice)</li>
            <li>Two-way SMS &mdash; patient replies, your front desk sees it</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>2. Treatment-plan completion automation</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--tx-soft);">Tracks every diagnosed but unscheduled treatment. Triggers a follow-up sequence at 7 days, 30 days, 90 days. Routes to the front desk on reply. Owner dashboard shows treatment-plan completion rate by provider.</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Diagnosed-but-unscheduled tracking</li>
            <li>Timed follow-up sequences with patient education content</li>
            <li>Provider-level completion rate dashboards</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>3. Review velocity automation</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--tx-soft);">Post-appointment SMS review request, timed for the visit type (same-day for hygiene, 48 hours for restorative, 7 days for surgical). Negative feedback intercepted privately. Practices typically add 25&ndash;50 Google reviews in the first 90 days.</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Visit-type-aware review timing</li>
            <li>Provincial dental college / ADA advertising rules respected</li>
            <li>Negative feedback to private inbox before public site</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>4. After-hours call rescue</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--tx-soft);">AI receptionist answers after-hours calls, books emergency or new-patient appointments, sends SMS confirmation. Routes complex calls to a human callback. Eliminates the "competing-chain has 24/7 booking" disadvantage.</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>After-hours, weekends, lunch coverage</li>
            <li>Trained on your services, hours, fee schedule</li>
            <li>Emergency triage routing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-card">
          <h3>5. Owner dashboard</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--tx-soft);">One screen: hygiene recall response rate, dormant-patient revenue recovered, treatment-plan completion rate, review velocity, after-hours bookings recovered. Monthly PDF for the practice meeting.</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Weekly + monthly KPIs</li>
            <li>Per-provider, per-hygienist breakdown</li>
            <li>Recovered-revenue calculation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-card" style="border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-soft);">
          <h3 style="color:var(--accent);">Built around your PMS, not replacing it.</h3>
          <p>Your team keeps using Open Dental, Dentrix, ClearDent, or Curve exactly the way they do today. We integrate as a layer on top. The front desk doesn&rsquo;t learn a new tool. Our system fills the gaps your PMS was never designed to fill.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Engagement shapes -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">Engagement shapes</p>
      <h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:8px;">Three shapes. Audit first. Most dental practices start with a Pilot.</h2>
      <p style="text-align:center;color:var(--tx-soft);margin-bottom:32px;max-width:640px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
        Engagements typically range from low-four-figures to mid-four-figures monthly (USD). With dormant lists worth $500K&ndash;$1.5M, the math pays back fast.
      </p>
      <div class="ai-tiers">

        <article class="ai-tier">
          <h3>1. Free Growth Audit</h3>
          <p class="ai-tier-tagline">Diagnose, free</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price" style="font-size:24px;">Free</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price-sub">30 min &middot; one-page leak report in 24 hrs</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Live walk-through of your Open Dental / Dentrix / ClearDent / Curve</li>
            <li>Dormant-patient list size + recoverable revenue estimate</li>
            <li>Treatment-plan completion rate analysis</li>
            <li>One-page leak report ranked by recoverable revenue</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="ai-btn-ghost" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">Book audit &rarr;</a>
        </article>

        <article class="ai-tier ai-tier-featured">
          <h3>2. Pilot</h3>
          <p class="ai-tier-tagline">Most dental ops start here</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price" style="font-size:24px;">60 days, fixed scope</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price-sub">See dollar impact before any monthly commitment</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Dormant-patient reactivation sweep wired to your PMS</li>
            <li>Treatment-plan completion automation live</li>
            <li>Post-appointment review automation</li>
            <li>Weekly check-in for 60 days</li>
            <li>End-of-pilot dollar-impact report</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="ai-btn" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">Book audit &rarr;</a>
        </article>

        <article class="ai-tier">
          <h3>3. Run-It</h3>
          <p class="ai-tier-tagline">Done-for-you, end-to-end</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price" style="font-size:24px;">Monthly retainer</p>
          <p class="ai-tier-price-sub">Cancel any time after first 90 days</p>
          <ul class="ai-checklist">
            <li>Full lifecycle: recall, reactivation, treatment plans, reviews, after-hours</li>
            <li>AI voice receptionist 24/7</li>
            <li>Custom integrations with your specific PMS</li>
            <li>Dedicated ops contact, weekly check-in</li>
            <li>Quarterly strategy session with senior operator</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="ai-btn-ghost" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">Book audit &rarr;</a>
        </article>

      </div>
      <p style="text-align:center;color:var(--tx-soft);margin-top:24px;font-size:14px;">RCDSO &middot; ADA &middot; provincial dental college advertising rules respected. HIPAA BAA on request. Full pricing on the audit call.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="ai-section-tight">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2>30-min audit. We pull your dormant list. We tell you what it&rsquo;s worth.</h2>
      <p class="ai-lead">No deck, no pitch. The leak report is yours to keep even if you never hire us.</p>
      <div class="ai-cta-row">
        <a class="ai-btn" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book the audit &rarr;</a>
        <a class="ai-btn-ghost" href="/about/">About the team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
